<plot>K has a loving daughter; born in Korea, speaking the language but with a different skin tone. As her interracial daughter faces discrimination and hardships, K comes to America in pursuit of dreams with hope. Her life starts off in a new place where she knows no one. Other difficulties await for the woman who expected a problem free life. Would K be able to keep the promise that she made with her daughter? In the harsh reality, will a day without tears come to her?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?354729</url></doc>
